

First connection to Pepper :

let's ssh
ssh nao@....

Qicli :
http://doc.aldebaran.com/libqi/guide/qicli.html

# change robots name 
$ qicli call ALSystem.setRobotName NAME 
$ qicli call ALStore.update
$ qicli call ALSystem.reboot


# change robots language :
$ qicli call ALDialog.setLanguage French
$ qicli call ALTextToSpeech.setLanguage French
$ qicli call ALSpeechRecognition.setLanguage French


Common path :
# nao user root dir
/home/nao

# package installation dir
/home/nao/.local/share/PackageManager/apps/
qicli call ALBehaviorManager.install package.pkg

